<h3>About Me</h3>
<p>
  I am currently a Postdoctoral Scholar in the
  <a href="https://math.as.uky.edu/topology-and-geometry">topology group</a>
  at the
  <a href="https://math.as.uky.edu/">University of Kentucky</a>.
</p>
<p>
  I completed my Ph.D. in Mathematics at the
  <a href="http://www.math.virginia.edu">
    University of Virginia</a>
  in May 2017,
  under the supervision of
  <a href="http://math.ucla.edu/~mikehill/index.html">
    Mike Hill</a>.
</p>

<p>
  <a href="Bonventre-CV.pdf">Curriculum Vitae</a> (updated 06 Apr 2020).
</p>



